snippet.title: ModDaGod Tv
snippet.description:
ModDaGod TV is a creative & youth inspired online talent and entertainment channel showcasing unsigned and emerging talent.

We bring innovative reactions, competitions, fresh freestyles and behind the scenes footage and the latest music in the Urban world. Over 

Make sure you subscribe to get our latest videos delivered to your YouTube homepage. 

Stay tuned for more exciting content from ModDaGod Tv
